00:07:18.104 --> 00:07:19.739
to spend some time
with y'all.

00:07:19.839 --> 00:07:23.876
♪ Is it too late now
to say sorry, ♪

00:07:23.976 --> 00:07:27.713
♪ because I'm missing more
than just your body. ♪

00:07:27.813 --> 00:07:29.148
♪ Ooh, ooh. ♪

00:07:29.248 --> 00:07:33.119
♪ Is it too late
