I do when he's working.

00:08:19.665 --> 00:08:21.868
And the second that he asked
to actually put the time in,

00:08:21.968 --> 00:08:25.071
I was like, oh okay, now, we're
ready to go back to work.

00:08:25.171 --> 00:08:26.572
Justin: My life is
changing a lot.

00:08:26.672 --> 00:08:28.608
Getting married, getting
back in the studio.

00:08:28.708 --> 00:08:30.610
Talking about getting
married, like, just writing

00:08:30.710 --> 00:08:33.112
about the process and
just being creative with

00:08:33.212 --> 00:08:35.848
being in this new chapter,
and being happy about

00:08:35.948 --> 00:08:38.217
what I'm doing and not
like, I don't know,

00:08:38.317 --> 00:08:40.186
just being in a
good head space.

00:08:40.286 --> 00:08:41.821
Better head space.

00:08:41.921 --> 00:08:45.992 line:0%
♪ She want a
touch down. ♪

00:08:46.092 --> 00:08:49.161 line:0%
♪ Nah-nah-nah-nah
nah-nah-nah. ♪

00:08:49.261 --> 00:08:50.863 line:0%
♪ Nah-nah-nah-nah. ♪

00:08:53.732 --> 00:08:56.302
I think what's been
challenging over the years is

00:08:56.402 --> 00:09:00.640
a lot of the times I'd make
music and it would be for me.

00:09:00.740 --> 00:09:03.309
When the focus and goal is
about yourself,

00:09:03.409 --> 00:09:05.845
