00:09:39.812 --> 00:09:41.847
Hailey: I love to see
him do what he loves.

00:09:41.947 --> 00:09:45.351
Honestly, I feel like I'm here
to cheer him on and support him.

00:09:45.451 --> 00:09:48.588
The last time around when he
was doing the "Purpose" album,

00:09:48.688 --> 00:09:50.923
I was around for
a lot of that,

00:09:51.023 --> 00:09:52.959
but definitely not
as intimately.

00:09:53.059 --> 00:09:54.226
Justin: Oh, good
to see you, bro.

00:09:54.326 --> 00:09:55.227
- Good to see you too.

00:09:55.327 --> 00:09:56.195
Justin: I like your jacket.

00:09:56.295 --> 00:09:57.296
- Thanks, man.

00:09:57.396 --> 00:10:01.067
Hailey: I love to see him
do what he is so good at.

00:10:01.167 --> 00:10:03.069
Wee-hee-hee.

00:10:05.370 --> 00:10:07.340
There's a lot of pressure and
there's a lot of things

00:10:07.440 --> 00:10:09.675
