full process.

00:10:13.846 --> 00:10:15.348
Justin: So what have
we got up right now?

00:10:15.448 --> 00:10:18.951
Hailey: So me being somebody
who isn't a musician and,

00:10:19.051 --> 00:10:21.821
you know, is not involved
in music in that way,

00:10:21.921 --> 00:10:24.991
watching it, I have a whole
new found respect for Justin

00:10:25.091 --> 00:10:27.994
as well as other artists who
just put their blood, sweat,

00:10:28.094 --> 00:10:30.129
